Like Anita, we may need specific help to accomplish our ministry fully.

00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:28.840
For example, when it comes to making return visits and conducting Bible studies,

00:10:28.840 --> 00:10:34.840
could some brothers and sisters in your congregation help you to improve your skills?

00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:42.840
Likely, all of us would benefit by reaching out to such publishers who have gained experience

00:10:42.840 --> 00:10:45.840
and skill in those aspects of the ministry.

00:10:45.840 --> 00:10:51.840
What if you're a parent who wants to instill love for Jehovah in the heart of your child?

00:10:51.840 --> 00:10:56.840
How about asking some other parents or grandparents for advice?

00:10:56.840 --> 00:11:02.840
If they've had success raising their children to love Jehovah and become baptized disciples,

00:11:02.840 --> 00:11:07.840
they will certainly be happy to share their experience with you.

00:11:07.840 --> 00:11:12.840
And what if we have age, limitations, or health concerns?

00:11:12.840 --> 00:11:17.840
We may need practical assistance that accommodates our needs.

00:11:17.840 --> 00:11:23.840
For example, at many Bethel homes, elderly and infirm brothers and sisters are still having a regular

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:25.840
and productive share in the ministry.

00:11:25.840 --> 00:11:27.840
Do you know how?

00:11:27.840 --> 00:11:35.840
Elders at Bethel arranged for younger publishers to join the elderly ones in letter writing and phone witnessing.

00:11:35.840 --> 00:11:40.840
One sister by the name of Nancy, who was nearly 90 years old at the time, said this.

00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:44.840
I don't view letter writing as just stuffing envelopes.

00:11:44.840 --> 00:11:46.840
