00:11:46.840 --> 00:11:49.840
People need to know the truth.

00:11:49.840 --> 00:11:51.840
How encouraging.

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:59.840
Did you know that in less than a year, one group of precious older ones devoted over 1,000 hours to the ministry,

00:11:59.840 --> 00:12:07.840
wrote over 6,000 letters, made over 2,000 phone calls, and placed over 6,000 pieces of literature?

00:12:07.840 --> 00:12:14.840
What good was accomplished by working together and what joy they experienced?

00:12:14.840 --> 00:12:22.840
Of course, we have to admit that it takes humility to acknowledge that we need help.

00:12:22.840 --> 00:12:25.840
But in this we can learn from Apollos.

00:12:25.840 --> 00:12:31.840
Though eloquent, though well versed in the Scriptures, he accepted the help that he needed.

00:12:31.840 --> 00:12:37.840
As a result, he benefited and all those that he would teach thereafter benefited.

00:12:37.840 --> 00:12:39.840
So here's the point.

00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:47.840
Can you think of someone like Priscilla or Aquila, who could give you the help you need?

00:12:47.840 --> 00:12:56.840
If so, why not explain your needs and ask that person to join you in the ministry or on Bible studies?

00:12:56.840 --> 00:13:02.840
Now, if you've been serving Jehovah for a time, are you in a position to help others?

00:13:02.840 --> 00:13:08.840
If so, we encourage you to be observant, take the initiative to offer assistance.

00:13:08.840 --> 00:13:15.840
If you see that a brother or sister would benefit from a kind suggestion, don't hold back.

00:13:15.840 --> 00:13:20.840
At an appropriate time, you might begin the conversation in a friendly way by saying,

00:13:20.840 --> 00:13:25.840
may I offer you a suggestion, or here's what I try to do.

00:13:25.840 --> 00:13:32.840
Remember, if we're kind and thoughtful like Aquila and Priscilla, likely our words and example

00:13:32.840 --> 00:13:38.840
will prove to be a blessing to help our brothers find joy in making disciples too.

00:13:38.840 --> 00:13:43.840
Well, in the second part of this symposium, what have we learned?

00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:49.840
First, our brothers are a gift from Jehovah to help us make disciples.

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:59.840
And second, when we work together and support one another, all of us can find great joy in our precious ministry.

